{"tid":1117229,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] LAST IDEA ラストイデア (7) - 免首抽遊戲！高自由度技能武器配搭 冒險尋寶動作RPG！","createTime":"2019-04-20T13:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T15:17:04.000Z","uid":10165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"733f04a335a9daa4f523cca6878c16e6fab7df8d","tid":1117229,"uid":10165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kT89CVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkT89CVU.jpg&h=77691165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方網站 : <a href=\"https://www.lastidea.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lastidea.jp%2F&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=e3f0603c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lastidea.jp/</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lastidea_rpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flastidea_rpg&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=8dbbe6e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lastidea_rpg</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6SmH9mR82nj28_NNg_rZvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC6SmH9mR82nj28_NNg_rZvA&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=bfbac6ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6SmH9mR82nj28_NNg_rZvA</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">官方上Famitsu果陣話《LAST IDEA》可能係平成最後一隻神GAME</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲簡介</span></span></strong><br />\n  SQUARE ENIX 旗下智慧型手機新作《LAST IDEA》於官方生放送中宣布，遊戲將於 2019 年 4 月 18 日（傍晚）正式上市。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zabvnrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZabvnrp.jpg&h=1c328222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《LAST IDEA》是一隻冒險尋寶動作 RPG 手機遊戲，玩家扮演一位新手尋寶獵人，與失憶的少女一起展開冒險旅程。遊戲不設轉蛋完素，家可以按照等級在「Treasure hunt」獲得各種裝備，透過升級技能強化自己能力，就連最強的裝備也可以在「Treasure hunt」之中獲得，遊戲打寶元素非常豐富。主打輕鬆操作的割草玩法。值得一提的是，本作搭載了全新開發的操作系統「SMACOMA（Smart Command）」，透過滑動、點擊等直覺上的操作，任何人都能輕鬆享受遊戲流暢的打擊感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S2Us87B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS2Us87B.jpg&h=f025b153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chGvnui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchGvnui.jpg&h=1920d81f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4h6Fsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4h6Fsf.jpg&h=a5808931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲特色</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">無轉蛋的尋寶 RPG</span></span></strong><br />\n營運團隊指出，《LAST IDEA》不存在所謂的「角色轉蛋」或是「裝備轉蛋」。玩家只能透過尋寶獲得符合等級的裝備，並且磨練玩家技能來變得更加強大，而遊戲中最高級的裝備也只能透過尋寶獲得。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45od4Gy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45od4Gy.jpg&h=2fadf1bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7pwRmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7pwRmz.jpg&h=aad0cab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SqspGz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SqspGz.jpg&h=4d7bcbf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">高自由度的自定義角色</span></span></strong><br />\n遊戲初期實裝的裝備超過 600 種，每件裝備都能透過尋寶獲得並賦予其隨機的效果（屬性）及性能，即便是相同名稱的裝備持有的特性也不見相同。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uV4rVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uV4rVp.jpg&h=282fae80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8id4Hc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8id4Hc.jpg&h=6ab75638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  玩家在推進故事的過程中將遇到被稱為「IDEA（イデア）」的角色，可以透過「IDEA」從 10 種以上的技能樹中學習 3 種技能，並將其設置成可操作角色。從體型、髮型、角色聲音、裝備到技能樹都可以自行組合搭配，養成符合自己喜好的角色。<br />\n（※裝備的稀有度包括 Normal、Magic、Rare、Epic、Legend 等等；技能樹則有劍、炎、弓、盾、雷、死靈、斧、槍、雙刀、冰等超過 10 種類型。）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qdpHX2j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqdpHX2j.jpg&h=4f7abde6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">佢唔似白貓龍絆抽左個角色就定晒形，佢主打自由組合技能樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如原本劍skill 可以裝備雙手闊劍，再學斧 skill 剛力可以單手拎闊劍，再學雙刀 skill 變拎雙闊劍<br />\n或者學雙刀+火+雷就會幫左右雙刀附火附雷<br />\n唔單止外形有變，技能都有變，例如弓+槍可以變每支箭都貫通，弓+雙刀可以射到人出血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">By<span style=\"color: blue;\">有翅膀的黑貓</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D4XYSx-UcAAtV-W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD4XYSx-UcAAtV-W.jpg&h=e266c086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">以直覺操作的流暢戰鬥系統「SMACOMA」</span></span></strong><br />\n本作搭載了全新開發的操作系統「SMACOMA（Smart Command）」，透過滑動、點擊等直覺上的操作，任何人都能輕鬆享受遊戲流暢的打擊感。此外，玩家可以自行設置指定動作施放想使用的技能，以最習慣的配置打倒敵人，體驗以直覺操作的戰鬥系統。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L95W2u0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL95W2u0.jpg&h=30ee3b92&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4 人同時遊玩 &amp; 全玩家參與的拍賣會</span></span></strong><br />\n製作團隊指出，玩家可以招募其他同伴，前往高難度地城或是藏寶地點中尋找沉睡的「貴重寶物」。與同伴們發現的稀有裝備除了自己使用之外，還可以透過由全玩家參加的拍賣會賺取大筆金錢，而遊戲內獲得的裝備幾乎都能至拍賣會進行買賣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhc6Fg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffhc6Fg3.jpg&h=4aa689c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BfHndB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBfHndB4.jpg&h=465d2c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">全語音動畫享受故事劇情</span></span></strong><br />\n配合本作主線故事的行進過程，官方也會隨時更新故事的演出動畫，將邀請到實力堅強的豪華聲優陣容，以全語音的方式展開本作的動畫劇情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBUT4Ky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBUT4Ky.jpg&h=c9b88351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">景山將太 x 遊戲音樂交響樂團 JAGMO 所演奏的 BGM</span></span></strong><br />\n遊戲內的音樂將由景山將太作曲，並邀請到遊戲音樂交響樂團 JAGMO 來為其演奏。景山將太為日本作曲家，曾製作過《Pokemon X／Y（ポケットモンスター X／Y）》、《任天堂明星大亂鬥 X（大乱闘スマッシュブラザーズ X）》等知名遊戲的配樂；而 JAGMO 為專門演奏遊戲音樂的交響樂團，全名為 JApan Game Music Orchestra，曾舉辦過多場演奏會，並透過電視節目等手段向大眾傳播遊戲音樂，本次是其初次參與遊戲的製作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fAk4rYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfAk4rYC.jpg&h=0b96af77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 角色技能展示</span></span></strong><br />\nオーラのイデア「スカーレット」CV：内田真礼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2G4nRmCxG0I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2G4nRmCxG0I&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=c27cd9ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2G4nRmCxG0I</a><br />\n剣のイデア「ラグナス」CV：松岡禎丞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f7I3KJFjJp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df7I3KJFjJp4&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=efd349e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f7I3KJFjJp4</a><br />\n炎のイデア「アンジェリカ」CV：鬼頭明里<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w0o8nRRQS5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw0o8nRRQS5Q&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=48233f51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w0o8nRRQS5Q</a><br />\n槍のイデア「キーラ」CV：日笠陽子<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l_Sb-yrOczE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl_Sb-yrOczE&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=d1e23325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l_Sb-yrOczE</a><br />\n死霊のイデア「ヴ・マ」CV：土師孝也<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdnrHqIapiQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAdnrHqIapiQ&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=27eded61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdnrHqIapiQ</a><br />\n弓のイデア「ロウェナ」CV：桑原由気<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2U-YuyBLyt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2U-YuyBLyt0&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=7140553b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2U-YuyBLyt0</a><br />\n二刀のイデア「マチルダ」CV：水瀬いのり<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=83ihRefbUvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D83ihRefbUvs&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=6fd86524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=83ihRefbUvs</a><br />\n雷のイデア「カルム・メルム」 CV：小澤亜李<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rMdg6PZp6no\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrMdg6PZp6no&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=5b9db7cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rMdg6PZp6no</a><br />\n斧のイデア「バルディオス」 CV：大塚明夫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9ZVv9KK8LI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz9ZVv9KK8LI&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=0ff5bf52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9ZVv9KK8LI</a><br />\n氷のイデア「イリーナ」CV：小松未可子<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0OQLQahvVrs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0OQLQahvVrs&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=d1214f90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0OQLQahvVrs</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲畫面</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PFd8jYwaf4Y&amp;t=957s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPFd8jYwaf4Y%26t%3D957s&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=745de774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PFd8jYwaf4Y&amp;t=957s</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tVgien.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tVgien.jpg&h=5448ad9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEFj0fA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEFj0fA.jpg&h=e54d7282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gbZ8TBG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgbZ8TBG.jpg&h=f5272057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8H6vnvp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8H6vnvp.jpg&h=27fbb8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DCOBh3L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDCOBh3L.jpg&h=6a81d6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS：<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1437222508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1437222508&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=db0f8732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1437222508</a><br />\nAndroid：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.square_enix.android_googleplay.lastidea&amp;hl=hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.square_enix.android_googleplay.lastidea%26hl%3Dhk&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=22ca3b43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.square_enix.android_googleplay.lastidea&amp;hl=hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/7434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F7434&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=914cdde1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/7434</a>"},{"pid":"2e3d8bf7f46d78aca845356cf43eae7c384ce5e4","tid":1117229,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:05:15.000Z","msg":"想問下死靈加盾會有咩效果？"},{"pid":"bdb5fa3bf7240fc33cf7e69662eb35d603d64721","tid":1117229,"uid":192390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:17:04.000Z","msg":"仲以為第2隻角色可以再創隻新<br />\n男角好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}